    /**
     * @description Allows access to resources collection, scoped to coachId.
     * @path /databases/(default)/documents/resources/{resourceId}
     * @allow (get, list) Only users who are owners (coachId matches).
     * @allow (create) Only users who are owners (coachId matches).
